title: Dark Souls Prepare to Die Edition Re-upload
description:
Dark Souls: Prepare to Die Edition (PC)

Description: With tense dungeon crawling and fearsome enemy encounters, the seamlessly intertwined world of Dark Souls is full of extreme battles, rewarding challenges, nuanced weaponry and magic, and the flexibility to customize each character to suit any desired play style. The innovative online component allows gamers to draw from the collective experience of the Dark Souls community as they either help or sabotage each other on the journey through the world of Lordran to save the land from darkness. With a massive, seamless open world design, Dark Souls encourages deep exploration and an adaptable gameplay experience.

Release Date: Aug 24, 2012
Publisher: Namco Bandai Games America
Developer: From Software
Genre: Role-Playing
ESRB Descriptors: Blood and Gore, Partial Nudity, Violence
